name: Olympus Part 1

Tinkle Presents: The Adventures of Suppandi

description: Sidonia's house is destroyed in an explosion. Luckily, Sidonia, Suske and Wiske can stay at Lambik and Jerom. Sidonia takes a sidejob, but is accused of stealing. Then a bank is robbed and the security cameras have footage of the culprit: again Sidonia. What's happening? When Lambik and Jerom find stolen stuff in her room, even Suske and Wiske begin to suspect their aunt...
name: Krimsonia

description: An unsuccesful architect wants to get famous and gets the help of the devil. He promises him a design that will make him famous. But the architect cheats and lets Lambik sign the contract. Lambik has disappeared the next day. And just outside the city, Lambik has surrected a bizarre house... Our friends took a look and discover many strange things. Lambik is under the control of a dark power who doesn't want to let him go without a fight.
name: Het Bizarre Blok

description: One day, Suske and Wiske get a lolly from a robot. It changes them into candy: Wiske turns into a gummybear and Suske is made out of chocolate. Soon they are kidnapped by the robot and taken to Suchardia, the Candyland. There they have to work in a gigantic candy factory. The land is terrorized by an evil wizard and a giant cotton candy. Suske and Wiske try to convince the king to defend it's citizens. But that's not done without a fight!
name: De Suikerslaven

description: Suske receives the diary of his greatuncle Cois Antigoon. In it is described how he, as a young boy in 1914, is sent to a boarding-school in Amsterdam, while his father was fighting in the First World War. Cois soon becomes friends with little Willemien. Together they rebel against the stern educator Ina. When Cois discovers the secret of Ina by accident, she turns his life into a living hell. He decides to run away. Drifting in Amsterdam, he meets Johnny, a vagrant. Their happy companionship ends in terrible treason and before he knows it, Cois is in deep trouble...
name: Suske De Rat

description: An experiment with ion radiation gets out of hand and Schanulleke changes into a superbeing, while Jerom temporarily looses his powers! Schanulleke decides to become a superhero and perform good deeds. But then the dangerously mental Boktor discovers the secret of Schanulleke's power. He kidnaps Wiske and wants to trade her for the ion canon. It comes to a big fight and everything seems to go to hell, but then help arrives from an unsuspected corner...
name: De Tirannieke Tor

description: Lambik rediscovers his old love for fencing. When he is challenged to an important duel, he doesn't want to loose and goes off in search for a magical rapier. It makes everyone that uses it invincible. Lambik arrives in the year 1680, the glory period of the musketeers. But his search isn't going too well: a gang of black musketeers are on his heels, a mysterious knights wants the rapier for himself and an army undead soldiers doesn't know when to quit... An album full of noble fencing and exciting fights!
name: Het IJzeren Duel

description: Suske and Wiske are rafting in South America and meet two men who lost their raft after an accident. Our heroes take them on board, but soon the gentlemen are not as innocent as the seem. They're searching for the God of the River, a gold statue that's somewhere in a holy indian resting place. Therefor they not only need our friends raft, but also their indian guide. The villains kidnap Suske and Wiske, but the indians guard their possessions and even the God of the River seems like a tough opponent.
name: De Vliegende Rivier

description:
Tsuzuki and Hisoka are still caught up in the horror at the university as the evil Dr. Muraki's diabolical cloning experiments continue. Muraki has joined forces with a modern-day Frankenstein in order to resurrect an old enemy and exact a vicious revenge. When Tsuzuki tries to interfere, Muraki takes his mind and body captive. Can Hisoka rescue him from the doctor's clutches before Tsuzuki's final act of desperation destroys them all?

Chapter 24 - 27 & bonus story Professor Watari's Road To Discovery.
name: Vol. 8

volume.name: Captain Jolly and His Pirate Crew

description: THE ANCIENT BOOK OF MYTH AND WAR presents to you a time capsule, a glimpse into a strange and wondrous world, where myths and legends still roam freely and wars rage in the hearts and minds of the noble and the feeble alike. Experiments in color, shape, line and composition enrich each and every page, accompanied by text that will enlighten the audience with atmospheric facts concerning origins, eras, and even media used in the production of the art itself. THE ANCIENT BOOK OF MYTH AND WAR is a fine art hardcover collection of images produced by some of the most highly sophisticated animation designers in the industry.
name: HC

volume.name: Ancient Book of Myth and War

description: He never should've taken the Devil's silver. Now his wife's passed away, and though Joe fears the worst -- that she's trapped in Hell, a captive of El Diablo -- he's determined to find her and deliver her from the Devil's clutches, whatever the cost. Aided by a down-and-out repairman and a little girl with a tragic secret, Joe follows a path that leads him through the afterlife and beyond. A God? Myth? Man? Well, who can know? Not a soul, but Ancient Joe...
name: TPB
